Revelation 16-3 <pb/>The second angel poured out his bowl into the sea, and <f>ⓕ</f>it became like the blood of a corpse, and <f>ⓖ</f>every living thing died that was in the sea.
Revelation 16-4 <pb/>The third angel poured out his bowl into <f>ⓗ</f>the rivers and the springs of water, and <f>ⓘ</f>they became blood.
